 />\n有私怨就有私怨，唔投就係唔投。"},{"pid":"51c29ea0f035737a278189f80eaecad3a3a72aba","tid":2105781,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e85e391413752047c9b57822bd38190aa197fbb","tid":2105781,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"892525751855c355a6cbfd0e10d019e005aa3a2c","tid":2105781,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:18:44.000Z","msg":"一早開工分化<br />\nSIR<br />\n<br />\nVenus 點"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:20:11.000Z","msg":"分咩撚嘢化 <br />\n我識快B快B識我。<br />\n有私怨就有私怨，唔投就係唔投。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:22:18.000Z","msg":"好撚老實，若果有三票你就要我分一票畀快B<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔撚會分，咁首先係我唔接受同我屋企人都唔接受嘛。<br />\n<br />\n所以我咪就係討論緊究竟個初選反唔反應到民意囉。<br />\n個結果有幾多人真係會尊重<br />\n你胡志偉唔撚入閘好多人唔識投"},{"pid":"a4665a8e8e1bce0921e9d0307c0f6bd0a52a1a59","tid":2105781,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e85e391413752047c9b57822bd38190aa197fbb","tid":2105781,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"892525751855c355a6cbfd0e10d019e005aa3a2c","tid":2105781,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:18:44.000Z","msg":"一早開工分化<br />\nSIR<br />\n<br />\nVenus 點"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:20:11.000Z","msg":"分咩撚嘢化 <br />\n我識快B快B識我。<br />\n有私怨就有私怨，唔投就係唔投。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:22:26.000Z","msg":"收工啦Sir"},{"pid":"530e9073d7225923fd198b4f0ebbcc583279c677","tid":2105781,"uid":224741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e85e391413752047c9b57822bd38190aa197fbb","tid":2105781,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"892525751855c355a6cbfd0e10d019e005aa3a2c","tid":2105781,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:18:44.000Z","msg":"一早開工分化<br />\nSIR<br />\n<br />\nVenus 點"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:20:11.000Z","msg":"分咩撚嘢化 <br />\n我識快B快B識我。<br />\n有私怨就有私怨，唔投就係唔投。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:23:07.000Z","msg":"泛登講真話會比